text: Raghuvansh Prasad Singh (6 June 1946 â€“ 13 September 2020) was an Indian politician. In the Lok Sabha, represented the Vaishali constituency of Bihar between 1996 to 2014. He was the national vice president of the Rashtriya Janata Dal political party until 2010. He was born in Vaishali, Bihar. Singh died of COVID-19 on 13 September 2020 in New Delhi at the age of 74. ==References== Category:1946 births Category:2020 deaths Category:Deaths from the COVID-19 pandemic in New Delhi Category:Bihari politicians Category:Members of the Lok Sabha
